      "review_summary": "The PR changes OpenAI Batch status, ChatGPT OAuth token, and Realtime client-secret success-response reads from raw response buffering/parsing to bounded shared response helpers.\n\nPR surface: Source +10. Total +10 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: Source-level yes, live changed-path no. Current main reaches raw `response.json()` and `arrayBuffer()` in the targeted OpenAI paths, and the bounded reader contract is clear from source, but this review did not establish a live provider repro.",
